{"tid":2426242,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"人民日报评爱国者达叔永远都是主角","createTime":"2021-02-28T02:59:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-28T08:11:36.000Z","uid":48419,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"09481bf214b2dca9c6ac4a9dc1f2437be8189bee","tid":2426242,"uid":48419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T02:59:11.000Z","msg":"#人民日报评爱国者达叔永远都是主角#【#人民锐评#：#爱国者达叔永远都是主角#】&ldquo;达叔走了&hellip;&rdquo;知名喜剧演员吴孟达2月27日在香港病逝，让香港和内地的很多网友陷入悲痛之中。他生前留下的最后一条微博写着&ldquo;我是中国人&rdquo;，令无数网友集体致敬。<ins><strong>然而，就是这种最纯粹的爱国情感，居然也能戳中香港一些宵小之徒的痛处。这些人越是攻击爱国者，越反衬出达叔心怀大义；</strong></ins>越是恼羞成怒，越说明达叔人格高大。在香港这个舞台，爱国者达叔，和那些热爱国家的人，永远都是主角。<a href=\"http://t.cn/A6tSiF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.cn%2FA6tSiF&d=zAz8RNAQ9Ot7v23HNjWT3gUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=ce2b6fb0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.cn/A6tSiF</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/skmYx2z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FskmYx2z.png&h=3ad06182&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eccb26d05f360a6758ae9fc16e0410c60814d8ae","tid":2426242,"uid":40397,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T03:02:49.000Z","msg":"肯出幾篇野就真係可以返大陸撈到風生水起<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔怪得咁多偽人肯出我是中國人，一點都不能少個d post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"484ac4380c8e7daf3abe6bb12697aa4a90954171","tid":2426242,"uid":58630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T03:05:27.000Z","msg":"希望佢下世都做到中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a602300b1bb0d22ef455b3356940e1a19c44ddf","tid":2426242,"uid":22310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T03:06:53.000Z","msg":"19年8月16 最後一條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\npo 親都係奶共先po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" clas